        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6">Common Michigan Furnace Failures Explained</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Ignition failures, dirty flame sensors, and blower motor issues are the top causes of no-heat calls. Knowing these helps you act before a full breakdown.</p>
