      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-red-600 text-white text-center">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Repair or Replace?</h3>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">If your furnace is over 15 years old or keeps breaking down, it may be time to upgrade. We‚Äôll guide you with a clear, honest recommendation.</p>
      <a href="/furnace-diagnosis" class="bg-white text-red-600 font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">Start Diagnosis Quiz</a>
